FILESIZE: 270 KB (276,568 bytes)
FILESIZE: 171 KB (175,675 bytes)
DATE RELEASED: 03 September 2008

CREDITS: Pure insperation

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Extract all contents of the .zip file directly into your "\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\YOURNAMEHERE\counter-strike source\cstrike\" folder.

DESCRIPTION: This map has a great space for gun to gun combat for those rushers. Includes boxes for dodging snipers or any enemy. Tall spawn bases for long range shooting. Also feature 30 T and 30 CT spawn points

COMMENTS: No third-party/third-person testing was done before the release of this map. If you have any problems, tell me on my FPSBanana page ("WEBSITE"), or e-mail me. Copyright 2008 Turtle Productions rights reserved.
